Your Nvidia driver and CUDA version is much newer than me and your problem seems like a widespread problem.
I will try the latest Nvidia driver version later. And there is a sure way to solve all the problem: Install [anaconda](https://www.anaconda.com/) and [pytorch](https://pytorch.org/). By the way, I search for this [question](https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/35803), it may cause by loss some ".dll".
